 * style.link_hover_color => 链接悬停颜色:color:#ff5a36
 * style.border_top => 显示顶部边框:select:yes|yes,no
 * style.border_color => 边框颜色:color:#ead6c8
 *
 * group:layout => 布局设置
 * layout.max_width => 最大宽度:number:1200
 * layout.padding_horizontal => 左右内边距:responsive:20/36|px[MD]
 * layout.padding_vertical => 上下内边距:responsive:34/56|px[MD]
 *
 * group:footer => 页脚品牌设置
 * footer.logo_text => 品牌名称:text:Three Patti Mela Pop
