 * footer.links => 页脚链接:textarea:Home|/,Blog|/blog,FAQ|/faqs,About|/about,Privacy|/privacy-policy
 * footer.copyright => 版权信息:text:© 2026 Three Patti Mela Pop | All rights reserved
 * footer.disclaimer_text => 免责声明:textarea:18+ Only. Play responsibly and review local gaming rules before participating.
